_sText:
This is a map geared more towards zombie mod (regular and horde) gameplay, if people seem to like it, I'll make a DE version. There are 50 terrorist spawns and 30 counter-terrorist spawns, terrorist spawn in the back and CT's spawn in the school and outside in the front. There are a few easter eggs, and the map is loosely based off of my school. There are three floors a basement, first floor, and second floor. 

The textures are included in the map, and it is 45 MB. (If anyone knows of a way to decrease the size, let me know without altering the actual map [except settings or adding something])
